Waraxe <br/>
<br/>
Average Length: Approx. <br/>
<br/>
Type of Weapon: Distanced Hand-to-hand.<br/>
<br/>
Commonly used by: <br/>
<br/>
The term waraxe is not a particular weapon but rather descriptive of<br/>
an axe designed specifically for use in combat. Waraxes were generally<br/>
all metal construction and occasionally double-headed.<br/>
Their axe heads were often longer and broader than a common<br/>
woodsman’s axe was.<br/>
